ning seasons. A selection of his original sketchbook drawings is included, along with thirty-five exquisite illustrations by naturalist and artist Debby Cotter Kaspari.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Feb 2020) 7aNATURE / Animals.2bisacsh1 aKaspari, Debby Cotter1 aWisner, Geoff, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYUP eBook Package 2017z978311063898140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300228069423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/doc/cover/9780300228069.jpg  a978-3-11-063898-1  YUP eBook Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles